    <!-- Help Text -->
    <string name="help_title">How it works</string>
    <string name="help_description">This app temporarily stabilizes GPU glitches by running
        intensive shader sequences that force the GPU to refresh its pipeline. The process is
        similar to what happens when you run a demanding game, but focused specifically on clearing
        display artifacts.

The reset sequence runs for 5 seconds and is safe for all devices. No
        root access is required.
    </string>

